  <body>
    <segment id="1">
Journey into the unknown
Reise ins Ungewisse</segment>
    <segment id="13" parent="2" relname="interpretation">

Today, the members of the Prignitz District Council must make a decision of some significance.
Eine Entscheidung von einiger Tragweite müssen heute die Mitglieder des Prignitzer Kreistages fällen .</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="19" relname="span">  

Because they occupy nothing less than the highest administrative position in the district.
Denn sie besetzen nichts weniger als die oberste Verwaltungsposition im Landkreis .</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="20" relname="span">  


The incumbent district administrator Hans Lange (CDU) is running against Margarete Vierjahn.
Der amtierende Landrat Hans Lange ( CDU ) tritt gegen Margarete Vierjahn an ,</segment>
    <segment id="14" parent="3" relname="e-elaboration"> 

who has gained the support of the SPD.
die sich die Unterstützung der SPD erworben hat .</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="15" relname="condition">


If the position were to be filled by a referendum like that of the full-time mayors, the result would probably be clear.</segment>
    <segment id="15" parent="18" relname="span"> 

the result would probably be clear.</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="24" relname="span">  

Because Hans Lange can expect great support, especially in the western part of the district.</segment>
    <segment id="6" parent="22" relname="span">  

With him, the citizen knows what he has </segment>
    <segment id="16" parent="6" relname="interpretation"> 

- or also does not have.</segment>
    <segment id="7" parent="23" relname="list">  

With some justification, one can also say that he has grown in his role.</segment>
    <segment id="8" parent="9" relname="concession">  

Margarete Vierjahn, on the other hand, undoubtedly has the qualifications for a higher administrative position.</segment>
    <segment id="9" parent="25" relname="span">  

But what she ultimately stands for, at least publicly, has not yet become entirely clear.</segment>
    <segment id="10" parent="27" relname="circumstance">  

However, the decision is ultimately made in the district council </segment>
    <segment id="27" parent="28" relname="span"> 

and is still open, </segment>
    <segment id="17" parent="27" relname="cause"> 

especially in light of a secret ballot.</segment>
    <segment id="11" parent="28" relname="interpretation">  

In this situation, the small factions play a key role due to the prevailing constellation.</segment>
    <segment id="12" parent="29" relname="interpretation">  

And so perhaps today the residents of Prignitz are facing a journey into the unknown.</segment>
